	<h2>What we Treat?</h2>
		At City Hospital Cancer Institute, we work-in-coordination with our 
		specialties of Medical and Haemato-Oncology, Radiation Oncology and Surgical Oncology 
		to provide the patients with a one-stop destination of solution for the disease.
		<br>
		<ul type="square">
		<li>Brain Tumour
		<li>Prostate Cancer
		<li>Liver Cancer
		<li>Lung Cancer
		<li>Breast Cancer
		</ul>
	</div>
