	<div class="How we Treat" id="HowweTreat?">
	<h2>How we Treat?</h2>
	City Hospital, through its research, combines various forms of treatment and medication 
	to provide quality medical services at affordable prices. It is backed by latest technologies
	 such as CyberKnife VSI, Tomotherapy and other advanced diagnostic and treatment technologies. 
	 We believe in adopting a comprehensive approach for every disease. Once the patient 
	 is bought to the hospital, our pool of doctors, scientists, and clinical researchers work 
	 together to defeat the disease. All cancers are treated at The City Hospital.
	 </div>
